inscription:
[A second inscription has been carved over an earlier one. The legible parts of the earlier one are here shown in {brackets}.]
{ST} IN MEMORY OF      {I}
EMMA DAUGHTER OF THOMAS
AND ANN FLETCHER OF
{N} HAWORTH WHO DIED MAY 30th
1852 IN THE 2-(?) YEAR OF HER AGE
ALSO IN MEMORY OF REBECCA
WRIGHT OF THE SAME PLACE
WHO DIED MAY 30th 1854
IN THE 58th YEAR OF HER AGE
{T}
{John}              {of Ha}
{worth}                {ye}
{10th}
THOMAS FLETCHER OWNER.
